headline: PKG Q3 Deep Dive: Greif Integration, Cost Pressures, and Industry Demand Headwinds
summary: Packaging Corporation of America (NYSE:PKG) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 6% year on year to $2.31 billion. Its GAAP profit of $2.51 per share was 11.4% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
